    <div class="info">
      <button id="info" class="">&#9432; How to Play</button>
    </div>

    <div id="infoOverlay">
      <div id="instructions">
        <h3>How to play</h3>
        <p><strong>Goal:</strong> Guess the pattern, in both order and color</p>
        <p>Insert your guess sequence into the empty sockets</p>
        <p>Hints are provided on the right side in the form of black and white pegs.
        <ul>
        <li><strong>Black peg</strong> corresponds to one peg from your color sequence that is both the right color and in the right
            position</li><br>
          <li><strong>White peg</strong> corresponds to one peg from your color sequence that is the right color but NOT in the right
            position</li>
        </ul>
        </p>
        <p>Please in <strong>every round</strong> enter <strong>Feedback</strong> in the textbox below after you chose your color combination.</p>
        <button id="close-info">Close</button>
      </div>
    </div>

